title: FC Akhtamar
text: FC Akhtamar (), is a defunct <a href="Armenia">Armenia</a>n <a href="association%20football">football</a> club from <a href="Sevan%2C%20Armenia">Sevan</a>, <a href="Gegharkunik%20Province">Gegharkunik Province</a>. The club was dissolved in early 1994 due to financial difficulties and is currently inactive from professional football.
